description	"Jedi Scout:
This vanguard member is physically weaker than other team members, but uses his speed and stealth abilities to achieve his objectives.

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber (Fast Style)
-- Saber Defense 2
-- 20% Less DMG

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (2)
- Push (1)
- Pull (1)
- Speed (3)
- Mind Trick (2)
- Absorb (1)

^8Attributes:
- BP Free Jumps
- Faster Movement
- Bunny Hop (2)
- Slow Faller
- Cortosis (1)
- Force Block/Focus (2)
- 1 Extra Life
"